  "detailed_description": "Purple Noise Echo is a dark neon atmospheric tactical game in which you play Node, a silicon entity who starts from nothing in a singular place where everything has to be discovered and understood.<br><br>It's a low pace game where you have to use your brain, not a gun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/e607a1a7dfa5b14880262a9ff67c598f.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>No past, no memory, no identity. <br>Start from nothing and discover what you can do along the way. Explore to understand the environment, and perhaps yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/fb0b09226dcfaca7bfe711b272ecf920.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>Move tiles up or down, unlock doors, create ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/ec530018d79f5606cd06611c8e9dedff.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>Alone, you’re weak. Surround yourself with entities, control them, give them skills. Are they allies our just tools?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/ffbcaef755a6142de4192a432af47d71.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>The path isn't straight and simple. Find how to get through the levels. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/154b71e92bfa904e393a380b0eae5753.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>Some will try to stop you and resources are limited. Think twice and use non-lethal strategies to make your way through.",
  "about_the_game": "Purple Noise Echo is a dark neon atmospheric tactical game in which you play Node, a silicon entity who starts from nothing in a singular place where everything has to be discovered and understood.<br><br>It's a low pace game where you have to use your brain, not a gun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/e607a1a7dfa5b14880262a9ff67c598f.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>No past, no memory, no identity. <br>Start from nothing and discover what you can do along the way. Explore to understand the environment, and perhaps yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/fb0b09226dcfaca7bfe711b272ecf920.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>Move tiles up or down, unlock doors, create ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/ec530018d79f5606cd06611c8e9dedff.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>Alone, you’re weak. Surround yourself with entities, control them, give them skills. Are they allies our just tools?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/ffbcaef755a6142de4192a432af47d71.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>The path isn't straight and simple. Find how to get through the levels. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085540/extras/154b71e92bfa904e393a380b0eae5753.webp?t=1685024919\" width=500 height=32 /></span> <br>Some will try to stop you and resources are limited. Think twice and use non-lethal strategies to make your way through.",
